          <h3>前端</h3>
          <p>React / Vue / TypeScript<br/>HTML / CSS / JavaScript</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <span class="skill-icon">🛠️</span>
          <h3>工具链</h3>
          <p>Vite / Webpack / Git<br/>Node.js / npm</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <span class="skill-icon">🎨</span>
          <h3>创意</h3>
          <p>交互设计 / 动画 / Canvas<br/>创意编程 / 可视化</p>
        </div>
